               <msContents>
                  <summary/>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i0">
                     <locus from="1v" to="18r">1v-18r</locus>
                     <textLang xml:lang="ar">Arabic</textLang>
                     <title ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT0049IHA#s35IHA">قران, Twenty eighth ǧuz’ (28/30)</title>
                     <incipit xml:lang="ar">
                        <locus target="#1v">-1v</locus>سورة المجادلة مكية. بِسْمِ اللّهِ الرَّحْمنِ الرَّحِيمِ. مائة واثنان وعشرون اية. قدْ سَمِعَ اللَّهُ قَوْلَ الَّتِي تُجَادِلُكَ فِي زَوْجِهَا وَتَشْتَكِي إِلَى اللَّهِ وَاللَّهُ يَسْمَعُ تَحَاوُرَكُمَا إِنَّ اللَّهَ سَمِيعٌ بَصِيرٌ<note>58:1</note>
                     </incipit>
                     <explicit xml:lang="ar">
                        <locus target="#18r">-18r</locus>رُّوحِنَا وَصَدَّقَتْ بِكَلِمَاتِ رَبِّهَا وَكُتُبِهِ وَكَانَتْ مِنَ الْقَانِتِينَ<note>66:12</note>
                     </explicit>
                     <note>58:1-66:12. Different handwriting from that found in the other manuscripts except in  IES04521K, IES04521M and IES04521O, which are written by the same hand.
Some of the words are divided into two different lines.</note>
                     <note/>
                  </msItem>
